\c 7
\s Ukusiliswa kwenceku yenduna
\p
\v 1 Kwathi eseqedile amazwi akhe wonke endlebeni zabantu, wangena eKapenawume\x + Mat. 8.5-13.\x*.
\v 2 Njalo inceku yenduna yekhulu ethile, eyayiligugu kuyo, yayigula isizakufa\x + Fil. 2.29.\x*.
\v 3 Kwathi isizwile ngoJesu, yathuma kuye abadala bamaJuda\x + 7.6. Mat. 8.5.\x*, imcela, ukuze eze asilise inceku yayo\x + Mat. 14.36.\x*.
\v 4 Kwathi bona, sebefikile kuJesu, bamncenga kakhulu, besithi: Yona kufanele ukuthi uyenzele lokhu\x + Tit. 3.13. Seb. 26.7.\x*;
\v 5 ngoba iyasithanda isizwe sakithi, njalo yiyo eyasakhela isinagoge\x + 5.14. 19.9. Eks. 18.4.\x*.
\v 6 UJesu wasehamba labo. Kwathi engasekhatshana lendlu, induna yekhulu yathuma abangane\x + 7.6. Mat. 8.5.\x* kuye, isithi kuye: Nkosi, ungazikhathazi; ngoba kangifanele ukuthi ungene ngaphansi kophahla lwami;
\v 7 yikho kangizibonanga ngifanele ukuza kuwe; kodwa khuluma ngelizwi, njalo inceku yami izasiliswa.
\v 8 Ngoba lami ngingumuntu obekwe ngaphansi kwamandla, ngilamabutho ngaphansi kwami, njalo ngithi kuleli: Hamba, njalo lihambe; lakwelinye: Woza, njalo lize; lencekwini yami: Yenza lokhu, njalo ikwenze\x + 8.49. Mark. 5.35.\x*.
\v 9 Kwathi uJesu ezizwa lezizinto wamangala ngayo, watshibilika, wathi exukwini elimlandelayo: Ngithi kini, angitholanga ukholo olungaka ngitsho lakoIsrayeli\x + 7.50. Mat. 9.2.\x*.
\v 10 Kwathi ababethunyiwe sebebuyele endlini bafica inceku eyayigula isisilile.
\s Ukuvuswa kwendodana yomfelokazi weNayini
\p
\v 11 Kwasekusithi nge\add langa\add* elilandelayo, waya emzini othiwa yiNayini; abafundi bakhe abanengi basebehamba laye, lexuku elikhulu.
\v 12 Kwathi esesondela esangweni lomuzi, njalo khangela, kwakulofileyo ethwelwe kuphunywa, indodana engeyodwa kanina\x + 8.42. 9.38. Heb. 11.17.\x*, futhi yena engumfelokazi; lexuku elikhulu lomuzi lalilaye.
\v 13 INkosi imbona, yasisiba lesihelo ngaye, yathi kuye: Ungakhali.
\v 14 Yasondela yathinta ithala; aba\add li\add*thweleyo basebesima\x + 2 Sam. 3.31.\x*; yasisithi: Jaha, ngithi kuwe: Vuka\x + Mark. 5.41.\x*!
\v 15 Ofileyo wasevuka wahlala waqala ukukhuluma. Yasimnika unina.
\v 16 Ukwesaba kwasekubabamba bonke\x + 1.65. Seb. 2.43.\x*, basebemdumisa uNkulunkulu\x + Mat. 15.31.\x*, besithi: Umprofethi omkhulu usevukile phakathi kwethu\x + 7.39. Joha. 6.14.\x*; lokuthi: UNkulunkulu uhambele abantu bakhe\x + 1.68.\x*.
\v 17 Le indumela ngaye yasiphumela kuyo yonke iJudiya, lakuso sonke isigaba esizingelezeleyo.
\s UJesu loJohane uMbhabhathizi
\p
\v 18 Abafundi bakaJohane basebembikela ngazo zonke lezizinto\x + Mat. 11.2-19.\x*.
\v 19 UJohane wasebizela kuye ababili abathile kubafundi bakhe wa\add ba\add*thuma kuJesu, esithi: Wena unguye ozayo yini, kumbe silindele omunye?
\v 20 Lamadoda esefikile kuye athi: UJohane uMbhabhathizi usithumile kuwe, esithi: Wena unguye ozayo yini, kumbe silindele omunye?
\v 21 Langalelohola wasilisa abanengi ezifweni lemikhuhlaneni lakubomoya ababi\x + Mark. 5.29.\x*, labayiziphofu abanengi wabapha ukubona\x + 7.42.\x*.
\v 22 UJesu wasephendula wathi kubo: Hambani limtshele uJohane izinto elizibonileyo lelizizwileyo: Ukuthi iziphofu zibuye zibone, iziqhuli ziyahamba, amalephero ayahlanjululwa, izacuthe ziyezwa, abafileyo bayavuswa, abayanga bayatshunyayezwa ivangeli;
\v 23 njalo ubusisiwe loba ngubani ongakhubekiyo ngami.
\p
\v 24 Kwathi sezihambile izithunywa zikaJohane, waqala ukukhuluma lamaxuku ngoJohane \add esithi\add*: Laphuma laya enkangala ukuyabonani? Umhlanga onyikinywa ngumoya yini?
\v 25 Kanti laphumela ukuyabonani? Umuntu owembethe izembatho ezicolekileyo yini? Khangelani, abe\add mbethe\add* ezikhazimulayo baphila mnandi basezindlini zamakhosi.
\v 26 Pho laphumela ukuyabonani? Umprofethi yini? Yebo, ngithi kini: Loba odlula kakhulu umprofethi.
\v 27 Lo nguye okubhalwe ngaye \add ukuthi\add*: Khangela, mina ngiyathuma isithunywa sami phambi kobuso bakho, esizalungisa indlela yakho phambi kwakho\x + Mal. 3.1.\x*.
\v 28 Ngoba ngithi kini: Phakathi kwabazelwe ngabesifazana kakho umprofethi omkhulu kuloJohane uMbhabhathizi; kodwa omncinyane embusweni kaNkulunkulu mkhulu kulaye.
\p
\v 29 Labantu bonke bekuzwa, labathelisi, bathi ulungile uNkulunkulu\x + 7.35.\x*, sebebhabhathiziwe\x + 3.12. Mat. 21.32.\x* ngobhabhathizo lukaJohane\x + Seb. 18.25; 19.3.\x*;
\v 30 kodwa abaFarisi lezazumthetho\x + Mat. 22.35.\x* balala icebo likaNkulunkulu\x + Seb. 20.27.\x* bemelene labo, ngoba bengabhabhathizwanga nguye.
\p
\v 31 Yasisithi iNkosi: Pho-ke abantu balesisizukulwana ngizabafananisa lani? Kanti bafanana lani?
\v 32 Banjengabantwana abancane abahlezi emakethe bememezana besithi: Silitshayele umhlanga, kodwa kalisinanga; silililele, kodwa kalikhalanga.
\v 33 Ngoba uJohane uMbhabhathizi wafika engadli isinkwa njalo enganathi iwayini, laselisithi: Uledimoni;
\v 34 iNdodana yomuntu ifikile isidla, inatha, laselisithi: Khangelani, umuntu oligovu lesinathi sewayini, umngane wabathelisi lezoni.
\v 35 Kodwa inhlakanipho ithiwa ilungile ngabantwana bayo bonke\x + 7.35.\x*.
\s Owesifazana oyisoni endlini yomFarisi
\p
\v 36 Omunye wabaFarisi wasemcela ukuthi adle laye; esengenile endlini yomFarisi wahlala ekudleni\x + Mat. 26.6-13. Mark. 14.3-9. Joha. 11.2; 12.1-8.\x*.
\v 37 Njalo khangela, owesifazana kulowomuzi, owayeyisoni, esekwazi ukuthi uJesu uhlezi ekudleni endlini yomFarisi, waletha umfuma \w we-alibasta\w** owamagcobo\x + Mat. 26.7.\x*,
\v 38 wasesima eceleni kwenyawo zakhe ngemva \add kwakhe\add* ekhala, waqala ukuthambisa inyawo zakhe ngenyembezi, wa\add ze\add*sula ngenwele zekhanda lakhe, wanga inyawo zakhe, wa\add zi\add*gcoba ngamagcobo\x + 7.44. Joha. 11.2; 12.3. Joha. 13.5.\x*.
\v 39 Kuthe umFarisi obemnxusile e\add ku\add*bona wakhulumela ngaphakathi kwakhe wathi: Lo\x + 15.2.\x*, uba ebengumprofethi\x + 7.16.\x*, ngabe uyamazi ukuthi ungubani lokuthi unjani lo owesifazana omthintayo, ngoba uyisoni.
\v 40 UJesu wasephendula wathi kuye: Simoni, ngilengizakukhuluma lawe\x + Mat. 9.4.\x*. Yena wasesithi: Khuluma, Mfundisi.
\v 41 Kwakukhona ababili ababelezikwelede kumkweledisi othile; omunye wayelomlandu \w wabodenariyo\w** abangamakhulu amahlanu, lomunye abangamatshumi amahlanu.
\v 42 Kwathi bengelakho okokuhlawula ngakho, wabaxolela bobabili\x + Roma 8.32. Luka 7.21,43. Seb. 25.11,16; 27.24.\x*. Kambe nguwuphi kubo, tshono, ozamthanda okwedlulisileyo?
\v 43 USimoni wasephendula wathi: Ngicabanga ngulowo amxolela okwedlulisileyo. Wathi kuye: Wahlulele ngokuqonda.
\v 44 Wasetshibilikela kowesifazana, wathi kuSimoni: Uyambona lo owesifazana yini? Ngingene endlini yakho, amanzi enyaweni zami kawu\add ngi\add*nikanga\x + Gen. 18.4. Hlu. 19.21.\x*; kodwa yena uzithambisile inyawo zami ngenyembezi zakhe\x + 7.38.\x*, wa\add ze\add*sula ngenwele zekhanda lakhe\x + 7.44. Joha. 11.2; 12.3. Joha. 13.5.\x*.
\v 45 Kawunganganga; kodwa yena, lokhu ngingenile, kayekelanga ukwanga inyawo zami\x + 2 Sam. 15.5. 2 Sam. 14.33. Roma 16.16.\x*.
\v 46 Ngamagcobo ikhanda lami kawuligcobanga; kodwa yena ugcobile inyawo zami ngamakha\x + Hlab. 23.5.\x*.
\v 47 Ngenxa yalokhu, ngithi kuwe: Izono zakhe ezinengi zithethelelwe, ngoba uthandile kakhulu; kodwa lowo othethelelwa kancinyane, uthanda kancinyane\x + 1 Tim. 1.14.\x*.
\v 48 Wasesithi kuye: Zithethelelwe izono zakho\x + Mat. 9.2.\x*.
\v 49 Ababehlezi laye ekudleni basebeqala ukukhulumisana bodwa \add besithi\add*: Ngubani lo othethelela lezono\x + 8.25. Mat. 9.3. Mark. 2.12.\x*?
\v 50 Wasesithi kowesifazana: Ukholo\x + 1 Tim. 1.14.\x* lwakho\x + 7.9. Mat. 9.2.\x* lukusindisile\x + Mark. 10.52.\x*; hamba ngokuthula\x + 8.48.\x*.